tags.note: Not an official park, but listed in the IDNR's Public Access Needs Assessment Appendices and owned by the Gary City Park and Recreation Board.

tags.name: Dallas Totlot
tags.note: There is considerable confusion about where this park actually is. IDNR says it’s here, at the corner of Dallas and 2nd. The City of Gary instead says it’s at 2600 Dallas, but simultaneously says it’s in Brunswick, so it contradicts itself.
